                        <p>From airport transfers to cross-country journeys, we provide reliable, comfortable, and safe transportation throughout Rwanda. Our modern fleet and experienced drivers ensure your travels are smooth and enjoyable.</p>
                        <ul class="service-highlights">
                            <li>Modern, well-maintained vehicle fleet</li>
                            <li>Professional drivers with local expertise</li>
                            <li>24/7 availability and support</li>
                            <li>Comprehensive insurance coverage</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-panel">
                    <div class="service-image">
                        <img src="/images/elephant.jpeg" alt="Cultural Heritage Tours in Rwanda" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <h3>Cultural Heritage Tours</h3>
                        <p>Immerse yourself in Rwanda's rich cultural tapestry through our carefully curated heritage tours. Visit historical sites, meet local artisans, and experience traditional ceremonies that showcase the country's vibrant traditions.</p>
                        <ul class="service-highlights">
                            <li>Authentic cultural experiences</li>
                            <li>Local community engagement</li>
                            <li>Historical site visits</li>
                            <li>Traditional craft demonstrations</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

